{"tid":2450773,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"拜登：拒接種新冠疫苗者是不愛國","createTime":"2021-03-17T15:45:28.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-19T09:11:27.000Z","uid":278587,"like":1,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"63ad55e32a48e79de740a45f285733be9e43f53a","tid":2450773,"uid":278587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T15:45:28.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=427798\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D427798&d=V7AID%2B4Ek1BfB0hSL70CT8RCHeky4xD%2FQbA%2BfbsvJuc%3D&h=3e95db89\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D427798&h=c525b399\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=427798</a><br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】美國總統拜登警告，如果民眾不採取防疫措施，美國可能難以在七月國慶日前放寬限制。<br />\n<br />\n拜登接受美國廣播公司訪問，坦言對新冠疫苗接種計劃被政治化感到驚訝，不明白為何有民眾仍然堅持，自己有自由和權利拒絕接種疫苗，形容這些不願意接種的人是不愛國。<br />\n<br />\n拜登說自己接種疫苗後，生活上最大的轉變，是可以擁抱孫兒；又警告如果民眾不聽勸告戴口罩、勤洗手，和保持社交距離，美國或者不能夠在七月四日美國國慶前，放寬防疫限制。<br />\n<br />\n美國國家過敏症和傳染病研究所所長福奇，出席眾議院聽證會時指，對疫情的發展審慎樂觀，認為仍然存在很多挑戰，包括要追蹤變種新冠病毒。雖然科學數據顯示美國現時使用的疫苗，對變種病毒有效，但民眾仍然要保持警惕。"},{"pid":"500b38ed95611647e712fb90b0bbaf095a1ff346","tid":2450773,"uid":376140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"63ad55e32a48e79de740a45f285733be9e43f53a","tid":2450773,"uid":278587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T15:45:28.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=427798\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D427798&d=V7AID%2B4Ek1BfB0hSL70CT8RCHeky4xD%2FQbA%2BfbsvJuc%3D&h=3e95db89\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D427798&h=c525b399\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=427798</a